"{\"uid\": \"ipsnews.net-2024-08-improving-childhood-health-development-need-not-olympian-effort\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Monday, March 23, 2026  A baby hangs on a scale during a community health check-up and vaccination in Akosombo in the Eastern Region, Ghana, on April 28, 2022. Credit: Gavi/2022/Nipah Dennis  GENEVA, Aug 7 2024  (IPS)- From 11-year-old Chinese skateboarder Zheng Haohao to 16-year-old American gymnast Hezly Rivera,several childrenhave reached the pinnacle of world sport at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akosombo_Dam\", \"score\": 0.9999998515800254, \"rank\": 1.484201774224068e-07, \"text\": \"Akosombo\", \"types\": [\"Q12323\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akosombo_Dam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akosombo_Dam\"}, {\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.183150991284074e-20, \"text\": \"Ghana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\"}, {\"begin\": 168, \"end\": 172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GAVI\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1672656617699853e-58, \"text\": \"Gavi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GAVI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GAVI\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henipavirus\", \"score\": 0.9997966956138569, \"rank\": 0.0002033456703018814, \"text\": \"Nipah\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henipavirus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henipavirus\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999661649930012, \"rank\": 3.382762814073145e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9999967114471887, \"rank\": 3.208066667798684e-06, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}, {\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999997822569877, \"rank\": 2.177426772422317e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.6778949294325479, \"rank\": 0.4567682837669669, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet at the same time, millions of other children worldwide are denied the chance to unlock their full potential simply because of a lack of access to basic nutritious diets and vaccines that prevent disease.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As young athletes impress and inspire global audiences, the Games are the perfect moment to reflect on how to level the playing field for all children.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Integrating nutrition and immunisation as the cornerstones of healthy development can be a game-changer, ensuring every child is able to reach their full potential in whatever field they choose.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The conditions for healthy development include both the absence of disease and presence of adequate nutrition, creating a virtuous cycle that allows children to thrive.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaccines trigger the strongest immunity in children who have healthy diets, while those who are malnourished are more susceptible to infectious diseases.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unconscionably, in this day and age, both malnutrition and preventable infectious disease claim the lives of millions of children every year.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Globally,more than 14 million childrenare un- or under-vaccinated - an increase of 2.7 million compared with pre-pandemic levels - while almosta quarterof children under five were stunted in 2022 as a result of inadequate diets.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, immunisation and nutrition interventions are proven to be amongst the most cost-effective approaches to help children survive and thrive.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One dollar invested in nutrition gives a rate of return of US$16, rising to US$35 for exclusive breastfeeding, while the return on investment of immunisation in Gavi-supported countries is estimated at betweenUS$21 and US$54per US$1 spent.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is especially important for low- and middle-income countries where immunisation rates are lowest, malnutrition is prevalent and resources are stretched thin.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest UN figures showmore than halfof unvaccinated children live in 31 countries exposed to conflict and other vulnerabilities, disrupting access to nutrition and health services.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.8247785339856167, \"rank\": 0.21244668573240996, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same children often miss out on both nutritional supplements and essential vaccines, meaning that integrated health services would solve two problems at once.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Integrated nutrition and immunisation can be achieved either in the same clinic or community health facility, or through the same health worker.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Uganda is one country that has taken proactive action towards integration, and plans to shift to integrated provision of nutritional supplements and vaccines based on learnings from several pilot programmes.\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2703, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.928369751797281e-20, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Action Against Hunger and partners in Somalia mounted an integrated campaign to address rising levels of malnutrition and disease during the prolonged drought in 2022, which affected 7.8 million people.\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somalia\", \"score\": 0.9999999996880433, \"rank\": 3.1206091078635033e-10, \"text\": \"Somalia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somalia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somalia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign reached more than 200,000 children with measles vaccines, deworming treatments and vitamin A supplementation, and screened more than 185,000 children under five for wasting.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the referral sites for severe acute malnutrition, the average cure rate was 83 per cent and malnutrition decreased significantly over the period of the campaign.\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If more governments were able to adopt and scale such levels of integrated service delivery as part of primary health care, more countries could achieve Universal Health Coverage to reduce preventable deaths, ill-health and malnutrition in children.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3636, \"end\": 3661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_health_care\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Universal Health Coverage\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_health_care\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_health_care\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the world celebrates the remarkable achievements of young Olympians, the international community also has a window to transform the future of millions of children worldwide.\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the 2024 Games to Gavi's replenishment and the2025 Nutrition for Growth Summit, which has followed the Olympics since 2012, world leaders have the chance to invest in research and partnerships to integrate nutrition and immunisation as the fundamental components of healthy development.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 4203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3935, \"end\": 3939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GAVI\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1672656617699853e-58, \"text\": \"Gavi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GAVI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GAVI\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the winning formula for more children to succeed - on the track, field and pitch, and in life.\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afshan Khan, UN Assistant Secretary General and Coordinator of the Scaling up Nutrition (SUN) Movement  Sania Nishtar, CEO of GAVI, the Vaccine Alliance  IPS UN Bureau    IPS is an international communication institution with a global news agency at its core,raising the voices of the Southand civil society on issues of development, globalisation, human rights and the environmentCopyright \\u00a9 2026  IPS-Inter Press Service.\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4315, \"end\": 4319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khan_Noonien_Singh\", \"score\": 0.9484983335745191, \"rank\": 0.04597280521519154, \"text\": \"Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khan_Noonien_Singh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khan_Noonien_Singh\"}, {\"begin\": 4321, \"end\": 4323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.8247785339856167, \"rank\": 0.21244668573240996, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 4444, \"end\": 4451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaccine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.109705108075393e-70, \"text\": \"Vaccine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaccine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaccine\"}, {\"begin\": 4452, \"end\": 4460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alliance_Party_of_Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9996918642948251, \"rank\": 0.00030823068217318713, \"text\": \"Alliance\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alliance_Party_of_Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alliance_Party_of_Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 4462, \"end\": 4465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inter_Press_Service\", \"score\": 0.9991182302550577, \"rank\": 0.0008764980314836567, \"text\": \"IPS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inter_Press_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inter_Press_Service\"}, {\"begin\": 4466, \"end\": 4468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.8247785339856167, \"rank\": 0.21244668573240996, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.-Terms & Conditions\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4771, \"entities\": []}]}"